title.newValue: Microsoft Viva: Meeting category insights coming to the Viva Insights app in Teams

description.newValue:
Meeting category insights can help you align time spent in meetings with your goals by giving you visibility into the categories of meetings where you spend your time.
More info: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/viva/insights/personal/teams/viva-teams-app
GA date: September CY2022
